    "name": "Dumble Payment — Real QA Suite",
    "description": "Exhaustive scenario tree for Payment. Service-to-service API only; all endpoints require system JWT (signed with SERVICE_JWT_SIGNING_KEY) except /actuator/* and /payment/webhooks/paymob (HMAC-verified). Designed against payment-service-decisions.html. Runner pre-seeds 6 JWTs: service / admin / expired / wrong-key / user / no-iss.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
